 that wouldn't go away. As an avid runner, he noticed his times slowing down significantly. After weeks of tests, the diagnosis came back as Hodgkin Lymphoma. </span> <span style=\"margin-top: auto; display: flex; align-items: center; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 20px; border-top: 1px solid #ddd; padding-top: 20px;\"> <a href=\"#\" style=\"background-color: #d32f2f; color: white; padding: 12px 24px; text-transform: uppercase; font-weight: bold; text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.9rem; border: none; cursor: pointer;\">READ HIS STORY</a> <a href=\"#\" style=\"margin-left: auto; color: #d32f2f; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 500;\">See All Community Stories &gt;</a> </span> </span> </span> <span id=\"story-3\" class=\"story-panel\" style=\"display: none; flex-wrap: wrap; width: 100%;\"> <span style=\"flex: 1 1 300px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 300px; display: block;\"> <img src=\"https://placehold.co/600x800/444/FFF?text=Joy\" alt=\"Joy\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; display: block;\"> </span> <span style=\"flex: 1.5 1 400px; padding: 40px; box-sizing: border-box; display: block;\"> <span style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 15px; margin-bottom: 5px;\"> <strong style=\"font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: bold; margin: 0; color: #333; display: block; line-height: 1;\">Joy</strong> </span> <span style=\"font-size: 1.1rem; color: #666; margin-bottom: 5px; display: block;\">Caregiver</span> <span style=\"font-size: 1rem; color: #666; margin-bottom: 30px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 5px;\"> <svg style=\"width: 14px; height: 14px; fill: #666;\" viewBox=\"0 0 384 512\"><path d=\"M215.7 499.2C267 435 384 279.4 384 192C384 86 298 0 192 0S0 86 0 192c0 87.4 117 243 168.3 307.2c12.3 15.3 35.1 15.3 47.4 0zM192 256c-35.3 0-64-28.7-64-64s28.7-64 64-64s64 28.7 64 64s-28.7 64-64 64z\"></path></svg> Los Angeles, CA </span> <span style=\"font-size: 1.05rem; line-height: 1.6; color: #444; margin-bottom: 40px; display: block;\"> Joy didn't fac